            <V n="text" t="variation">
              <U n="variation">
                <L n="variations">
                  <T>0xAE38E098<!--String: "Ha, I'm so flattered that you want me to tell you gossip after all that quest stuff I made you do. The problem is, I'm not that interesting of a person on my own and I don't want to say anything mean about other people. What I can say is that Gibbi Point has a lot of different personalities that are all over the map. Variety is the spice of life, isn't it?"--></T>
                  <T>0x180C82D1<!--String: "I love it when there are a lot of Sims at Getaways in this neighborhood. I have more Sims to talk to and more stories to tell. Though I think I've told the story about the Melody of the Geyser so many times that I'm starting to recite it in my dreams. Well, there are worse problems to have!"--></T>
                  <T>0xA43F184C<!--String: "Have you checked in on Raheel lately, over by the Old Firewatch Tower? I wonder how he's doing. We don't always talk as much as we used to, but then again our friendship was more about just spending time around each other. Do you have friendships like that? Some friends like to chat a lot about everything and anything, but other friends just like being around one another even when there's less to say. There's a lot of comfort in that. "--></T>
                </L>
              </U>
            </V>
            <V n="title" t="enabled">
              <T n="enabled">0x59044392<!--String: "Gibbi-Gibbi That Gossip!"--></T>
            </V>
            <E n="visual_type">SPEECH</E>
          </U>
        </V>
      </U>
    </V>
